Class AlertFeedSearchResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.alertfeedretrievalservice.transport.AlertFeedSearchResults

  • public final class AlertFeedSearchResults
extends Object
    Contains the AlertFeedInfos and other information that form the results of a search for alert feeds.

    3.0
